<h3>Gratings Focus</h3>
<p>
Gratings observations are used to monitor the HRMA focus.  The links below
show plots of zero order image and streak event PSF fits as determined by
HAK for various detector/grating combinations.  Only observations of point
sources are used.
</p>

<a href="./Focus/obslist">  List of observations used.</a>
</p>

