<h3>Gratings E/de vs. E</h3>
<p>
We plot E/dE vs. E for fits to detected lines with fwhm_error/fwhm less than 0.15 for the plus and minus arms of HEG, MEG, and LEG. 
</p>
<ul>
    <li><a href='./EdE/EdE_out/hetg_ede_plot.html'>Open HETG Eneergy - E/dE Trend page</a> </li>
    <li><a href='./EdE/EdE_out/metg_ede_plot.html'>Open METG Eneergy - E/dE Trend page</a> </li>
    <li><a href='./EdE/EdE_out/letg_ede_plot.html'>Open LETG Eneergy - E/dE Trend page</a> </li>
